section.backstage
  .backstage__wrapper
    .backstage__image
      img(src="./images/backstage-image.jpg", alt="")
    .backstage__content
      h2.title-h2.backstage__title The Backstage of the Wilderness World.
      p.text-normal.backstage__text The site was founded on the basis of a volunteer movement to protect and care for animals.
      h4.subtitle.backstage__subtitle How it works
      p.text-body The main goal is to help the animals, as well as the nature reserves and zoos where they are kept. We are currently working on video projects targeting pandas in China, eagles on an island near Los Angeles, alligators in Florida and gorillas in the Congo. These have a total of more than 1,500 mammals and reptiles.
